      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Feb 23, 2017</title>
      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-02-23/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Feb 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-02-23/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo price slashed as Verizon proceeds with buy&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The SEC reportedly opened an investigation into whether Yahoo should have informed investors sooner about two major data breaches.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://au.news.yahoo.com/technology/a/34464473/yahoo-slashes-price-of-verizon-deal-350-mn-after-data-breaches/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://au.news.yahoo.com/technology/a/34464473/yahoo-slashes-price-of-verizon-deal-350-mn-after-data-breaches/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Hillstone launches server breach detection system&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Hillstone sBDS solution is a key component of Hillstone&amp;rsquo;s Intranet security portfolio, protecting critical assets such as servers, and leveraging &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.networksasia.net/article/hillstone-launches-server-breach-detection-system.1487772197&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.networksasia.net/article/hillstone-launches-server-breach-detection-system.1487772197&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Global Physical Security Information Management (PSIM) Industry 2017 Market&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NewsMaker (press release) WiseGuyReports.com adds Physical Security Information Management (PSIM) Market 2017 Global Analysis, Growth, Trends and Opportunities &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.newsmaker.com.au/news/254823/global-physical-security-information-management-psim-industry-2017-market-growth-trends-analysis-and-forecast-to-2019&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.newsmaker.com.au/news/254823/global-physical-security-information-management-psim-industry-2017-market-growth-trends-analysis-and-forecast-to-2019&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Verizon&amp;rsquo;s Purchase of Yahoo Downgraded by $350 Million Due to Data Hacks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;based Yahoo have agreed to share certain legal and regulatory liabilities arising from data breaches incurred by Yahoo in recent months.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://patch.com/california/mountainview/verizons-purchase-yahoo-downgraded-350-million&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://patch.com/california/mountainview/verizons-purchase-yahoo-downgraded-350-million&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Verizon, Yahoo cut merger price by $350M after hacks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Under the amended terms, the data breaches or losses won&amp;rsquo;t be taken into account in determining whether a business material adverse effect has &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.information-management.com/news/verizon-yahoo-cut-merger-price-by-350m-after-hacks&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.information-management.com/news/verizon-yahoo-cut-merger-price-by-350m-after-hacks&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo relieved as Verizon plans to go ahead with takeover&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The deal had looked a little shaky after it emerged that Yahoo had not one but two data breaches in recent years. Late last year it was reported &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.irishtimes.com/business/technology/yahoo-relieved-as-verizon-plans-to-go-ahead-with-takeover-1.2985252&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.irishtimes.com/business/technology/yahoo-relieved-as-verizon-plans-to-go-ahead-with-takeover-1.2985252&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Verizon Gets A Deal On Yahoo&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some clarity about Yahoo&amp;rsquo;s investigations of the data breaches will come from its required filing of regulatory reports in the coming weeks.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.investing.com/analysis/verizon-gets-a-deal-on-yahoo-200176567&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.investing.com/analysis/verizon-gets-a-deal-on-yahoo-200176567&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;UTM9 Endpoint Device Control can&amp;rsquo;t unlock Exceptions&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Problem we have is, that when I put in an ecxeption for a testet Device &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://community.sophos.com/products/unified-threat-management/f/endpoint-protection-antivirus-and-device-control/88544/utm9-endpoint-device-control-can-t-unlock-exceptions&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://community.sophos.com/products/unified-threat-management/f/endpoint-protection-antivirus-and-device-control/88544/utm9-endpoint-device-control-can-t-unlock-exceptions&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;After data breach, Frederick schools adopt response policy&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;FREDERICK, Md.  The Frederick County school board has a new policy for responding to data breaches like the one that exposed Social Security &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/after-data-breach-frederick-schools-adopt-response-policy/2017/02/23/46a08d40-f9dc-11e6-aa1e-5f735ee31334_story.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/after-data-breach-frederick-schools-adopt-response-policy/2017/02/23/46a08d40-f9dc-11e6-aa1e-5f735ee31334_story.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Most hackers can steal data within 24 hours, study shows&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; familiar path of compiling data about incidents that have already taken place or highlighting trends and patterns in data breaches  these are clearly &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.computerweekly.com/news/450413616/Most-hackers-can-steal-data-within-24-hours-study-shows&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.computerweekly.com/news/450413616/Most-hackers-can-steal-data-within-24-hours-study-shows&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Healthcare firms plan to increase security spending&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The higher interest in improving security is likely due to a combination of increased awareness of both data breaches and risks of ransomware, as well &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.csoonline.com/article/3173367/metrics-budgets/healthcare-firms-plan-to-increase-security-spending.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.csoonline.com/article/3173367/metrics-budgets/healthcare-firms-plan-to-increase-security-spending.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Healthcare data breaches &amp;lsquo;mostly caused by insiders&amp;rsquo;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Targeting healthcare organizations remains about as easy as shooting fish in a barrel. The industry has one of the lowest rates of data encryption and &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://nakedsecurity.sophos.com/2017/02/23/healthcare-data-breaches-mostly-caused-by-insiders/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://nakedsecurity.sophos.com/2017/02/23/healthcare-data-breaches-mostly-caused-by-insiders/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Who Americans Trust, Don&amp;rsquo;t Trust with Credit Card Data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;National news coverage of data breaches at large financial institutions versus local coverage of breaches at community banks and credit unions may &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cutimes.com/2017/02/23/who-americans-trust-dont-trust-with-credit-card-da&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.cutimes.com/2017/02/23/who-americans-trust-dont-trust-with-credit-card-da&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cyber threats and cargo theft: Is your fleet at risk?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; Verizon conducts an investigative report every year that analyzes more than 2,000 confirmed data breaches and looks at global contributors.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://fleetowner.com/fleet-management/cyber-threats-and-cargo-theft-your-fleet-risk&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://fleetowner.com/fleet-management/cyber-threats-and-cargo-theft-your-fleet-risk&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Security Central: Verizon Acquires Yahoo at Slashed Price, Trump&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The VAR Guy According to the software company, data breaches involving business associates working with healthcare organizations almost doubled in 2016, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://thevarguy.com/network-security-and-data-protection-software-solutions/security-central-verizon-acquires-yahoo-slas&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://thevarguy.com/network-security-and-data-protection-software-solutions/security-central-verizon-acquires-yahoo-slas&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;If Security and IT Aren&amp;rsquo;t Talking, Your Sensitive Data is Suffering&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;According to the Ponemon Institute, 75 percent of data breaches are caused by malicious or careless behavior from employees. To proactively avoid &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://techspective.net/2017/02/23/security-arent-talking-sensitive-data-suffering/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://techspective.net/2017/02/23/security-arent-talking-sensitive-data-suffering/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Appeals Court Dismisses VA Data Breach Lawsuit&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Plaintiffs claimed that earlier reported data breaches at Dorn VAMC created an increased risk of future identity theft, and that there were costly &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://healthitsecurity.com/news/appeals-court-dismisses-va-data-breach-lawsuit&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://healthitsecurity.com/news/appeals-court-dismisses-va-data-breach-lawsuit&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Wolfberg Presents Strategies to Manage the Risk of Patient Data Breaches at&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;JEMS.com The EMS environment and the risks posed by the widespread use of portable electronic devices formed the backdrop of the EMS Today session, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.jems.com/articles/2017/02/wolfberg-presents-strategies-to-manage-the-risk-of-patient-data-breaches-at-ems-today-2017.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.jems.com/articles/2017/02/wolfberg-presents-strategies-to-manage-the-risk-of-patient-data-breaches-at-ems-today-2017.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

